re__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://digitalassets-cdn.thron.com/api/v1/content-delivery/shares/ivq4cm/contents/lo-98d4f33b-920c-44ff-93f5-8cd791975ebd/image/image.jpg?w=500&amp;h=500&amp;zoom=true&amp;fillColor=ffffff&amp;crop=product\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Fast&amp;Clean</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Indesit’s most effective cleaning performance in just 28 minutes* * Does not include a drying cycle.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://digitalassets-cdn.thron.com/api/v1/content-delivery/shares/ivq4cm/contents/lo-a19d0d0c-0380-4bae-a49b-1dffa0c0631f/image/image.jpg?w=500&amp;h=500&amp;zoom=true&amp;fillColor=ffffff&amp;crop=product\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Energy class E</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Savings are always guaranteed with Indesit. At energy class E, enjoy high performances at great energy efficiency.</span></div>\n</div>\n",
